name: the witch
description:
We lie to our parents all the time. The things we did in the summer and also in the winter were not the things that ordinary teenagers do: go to the beach, go to the sea, get together to watch TV, watch a movie. To think that the existence that seemed to be claimed as God's property could not be someone else's or someone else's is what we discovered over the years as we visited that window again and again.

photograph taken in Mar del Plata, Argentina. Torreon del monje.
